guide.egg.common.body=§6Common Pet Egg §rcan be made with §c2 sticks, 2 rotten flesh, and 1 egg §r. Place the egg and tap it to hatch a random §ccommon pet §r. Then craft a §bCommon Evolve Stick §rand interact with your §cbaby pet §rto grow it into a §cadult pet §r.
guide.egg.rare.body=§6Rare Pet Egg §rcan be made with §c2 sticks, 2 iron ingots, and 1 egg §r. Place the egg and tap it to hatch a random §crare pet §r. Then craft a §bRare Evolve Stick §rand interact with your §cbaby pet §rto grow it into a §cadult pet §r.
guide.egg.epic.body=§6Epic Pet Egg §rcan be made with §c2 sticks, 2 diamonds, and 1 egg §r. Place the egg and tap it to hatch a random §cepic pet §r. Then craft a §bEpic Evolve Stick §rand interact with your §cbaby pet §rto grow it into a §cadult pet §r.
guide.egg.legendary.body=§6Legendary Pet Egg §rcan be made with §c2 sticks, 2 netherite ingots, and 1 egg §r. Place the egg and tap it to hatch a random §clegendary pet §r. Then craft a §bLegendary Evolve Stick §rand interact with your §cbaby pet §rto grow it into a §cadult pet §r.
