guide.pets_tutorial.title=Pets Tutorial
guide.pets_tutorial.body=There are §a43 pets §radded to your game! Each pet follows you and has their own abilities. All pets have a §bpassive effect §r, combat ability, or both. To activate some abilities, you can sneak + interact with your pet to open a menu. Tap the §eabilities buttons §rto use its abilities. Most pets also include a §cstanding toggle §rso you can sit your pet, and an option to §dride your pet §ras well.
guide.baby_tutorial.title=Baby Pets Tutorial
guide.baby_tutorial.body=There are §a43 §rbaby pets added to your game! To hatch a baby pet, you need to craft a pet egg and place it in your world. When you punch the egg, it will hatch into a random pet based on the rarity of the egg you crafted. You can sneak and interact with your pet to open a menu with options like a §bstanding toggle §rand the ability to ride your baby pet. To grow your pet into an adult, you need to craft an §devolution stick §rbased on your pet's rarity. Interact with an evolution stick with your baby pet to evolve it into an adult and unlock new abilities for your pet!
